Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.08,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深く激しく　そっと優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:21.06,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突き動かして情熱に訴えて　ひとつになろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:33.48,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳いだ目線　不埒な彷徨えるエゴイズム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:38.80,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着飾った秘密のベール 脱がせてくれるのはあなた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露骨に躍った欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.37,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは私のドコが理由なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:47.25,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のナニに昂っているの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.62,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ待って！　少し妬けるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:56.30,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空より遠い　冥より深い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:01.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の城より舞い降りしFreaky Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.30,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death Sickleが指揮者ね　魅惑のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.54,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突き刺さる心の十字架に　何を誓って戯れようか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:20.39,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦らした指先　先駆けた誘惑の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.43,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糸を手繰って　すぐココに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:29.19,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心から溢れ出した　甘い蜜に愛を這わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.74,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reason why kiss　離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.08,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深入而激烈 輕盈而溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:21.06,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放掉這股撩人的激情 合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:33.48,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右飄忽的視線 搖擺不定的利己主義讓人又愛又恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:38.80,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褪下我身上這層秘密薄紗的人 會是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那露骨的熊熊欲火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.37,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為我的哪個部分而點燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:47.25,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是因為我的什麼而高漲難耐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.62,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦！差點被你燒著了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:56.30,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比天空還高遠 比冥府還幽深
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:01.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從黑暗城堡降臨的怪異女王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:08.30,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮者是鐮刀冥使 它奏響了魅惑的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.54,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著直直插入心中的十字架 該許下什麼誓言來捉弄你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:20.39,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人心癢難耐的指尖 呼之欲出的誘惑之滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.43,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收緊命運的絲線 讓你立刻來到此處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:29.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓愛吸附在從內心中滿溢而出的甜汁蜜液之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.74,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reason why kiss 永遠不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:09.87,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋なんてもうしないって　何回も心に決めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:14.84,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繰り返す性懲りもなく　それが恋だもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:22.07,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残念な結末だって　そんなこと気にしなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:26.99,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっとまた出会えるはず　赤い糸の先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:33.01,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠い未来の自分へ　捧げたいのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:41.93,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今この時をみんなで　全力で生きた証でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:48.56,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが歩いてきた道には　満開の花が咲くから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:54.99,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　輝いてなくちゃ嘘になってしまうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:00.78,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見るもの聞くものすべてを　僕らは分かち合えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.28,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　手をつないで行く　終わらない明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:09.87,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕多少次下定決心 再也不去碰什麼戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:14.84,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一次次不知悔改的重蹈覆轍 這就是所謂的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:22.07,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算結果並不如你所願 但是也不用太過於在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:26.99,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的邂逅一定馬上就會出現 就在鮮紅絲線的那一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:33.01,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於遙遠未來的自己 現在的我想要獻給她的..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:41.93,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是此時此刻大家一起 全力奮鬥過的證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:48.56,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們一路走來的這段旅途之上 開滿了遍地的繁花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:54.99,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 如果不好好閃耀一下的話約定不就成了謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:00.78,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為眼睛看到耳朵聽到的一切 我們都會彼此分享
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:06.28,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 手牽著手一起前行 去到那永不終結的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祝福你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為自己的所作所為感到自豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有..恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱撒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦 凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 怎麼了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 良介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:45.91,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(920,600)}第10話 天國的乳地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小良..一直都不肯醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都很擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果良介先生有個三長兩短的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟讓格拉姆的力量發動到那種程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算產生了短時間的能量缺乏也是在所難免呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那之後發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然產生了暫時的混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於我們及時把雷斯託軍派往人間界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後事態就得到了控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..這是我的錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼自責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果良介先生不打倒那個狂人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就會變得更嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小良拯救了世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全可以更自信一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦..既然美菜平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而世界也恢復原樣的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命只剩下2週了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 畢竟我們也已經找到了特異者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能得救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介先生 我做了粥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..我正好肚子餓了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說人間界的男士們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這樣的打扮會產生非比尋常的興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著真好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍裙的下面好好穿著..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是..泳裝？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也不可能光著身子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..這樣更有一番..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不了解男人心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依莉雅醬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 妳沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別..別小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和妳決出勝負之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事我都會活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可話說回來 跑一趟這裡可把我累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車也全部都停運了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件和手機也都沒信號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個狀況要持續到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是辛苦妳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 到客廳去坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有對良介說！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有自己的苦衷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 今天您還是請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是恕難從命呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良 吃完的鍋子..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 小良..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 我的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色..色色的書在那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃一下房間後..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是男孩子呢 會看那種書很正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我媽嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找的是手機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有電腦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去用的話用完歸位行不？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機和電腦都和衣服一起送進了洗衣機..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不..手機暫且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦再怎麼都會察覺吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人真是的..因為很冒失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒嘿~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒嘿~個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後梅爾洛發生了很多麻煩事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說現在沒空來幫我經營
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 承蒙各位照顧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就從公司提供的公寓中搬出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為在這邊的世界中也沒有其他熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間是有空餘的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要住是無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 良介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可話說回來..既然還能維持那個術式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說妳找到契約者了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算..算是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 我從剛才就一直很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的電視哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為這個月的生活費不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以賣掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賣也挑其他東西賣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒電視沒電腦又沒手機..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去網咖一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也很想知道昏睡的期間發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難..難得大家都湊在一塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來玩紙牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次輸掉的人要脫一件衣服如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩大富豪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽鬼牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是梭哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我不會輸的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然有牌運呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇家同花順！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..葫蘆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三條..而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莉薩菈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散牌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再..再脫下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這裡逃避的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有損雷斯託家的名聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉..莉薩菈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..居然出老千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 這是..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒嘿~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒過來就欣賞到好東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的內衣實在是相當之風騷..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始你就在自言自語些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的忌日還有兩週
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來履行我的職責了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是達爾尼婭·伊爾哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說妳是死神？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼稱呼隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然讓妳特地跑來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過實在抱歉 我的命看來還有救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:11:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..雖然不知道用什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她們說能以特異者的力量救我..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起這種事情..居然還想著要自己獨活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒告訴你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行徑..為這個世界帶來了多大的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小良告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是妳覺醒成特異者的關鍵要素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被認為來自於特異者的爆發性能量反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是三個月前梅爾洛在桃園學園察覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個月前 美菜對良介告白了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而之後特異者的力量的那次瞬間發動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜對良介發出了強烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟平時只不過回憶一下就能產生這麼多能量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當美菜對良介先生告白 促成一段戀情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特異者的力量應該就會完全發動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..裘兒醬..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換裘兒來支持美菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裘兒醬..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我隱瞞了真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是這短短一週中人間界所發生的種種慘劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達爾尼婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位女士是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梅爾洛看到過好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達爾尼婭·伊爾哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道她在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正對她的評價就是忠實執行所有職務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職務是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳..難不成對良介？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 讓他看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯..變成這麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為我破壞了傳送門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那麼多人..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一派胡言！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是為了讓你陷入絕望才..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是一派胡言..只要到外面去看看就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於雷斯託軍的抵達而讓外出禁令解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即便如此局勢還是十分緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達爾尼婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以讓我知道的事情就在外面發生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒..沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉薩菈 我們走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻雷斯託軍仍在戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變成這樣 責任在我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我也要去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 莉薩菈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多把能量用得一幹二淨的你 根本做不了任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不用過於愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們狩獵的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因王室的婦人之仁而茍活下來..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些早就該死的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就該死的人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是..這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當加賀良介走完自己的人生之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}我會本著認真嚴肅的態度去引導他的靈魂並從中獲取能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要妨礙我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓妳得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會拯救良介的性命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用特異者的力量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們甚至連準備工作都還沒做好對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在加賀良介壽命耗盡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這個家裏待著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得稍微吃一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不吃的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳 稍微看一下氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 妳還醒著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 真的這樣就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在的良介一定不肯讓妳們延長他的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想一想如何去度過兩人僅剩的時光比較好吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妳在誤會什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和良介不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳還真是..！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那只色狼介..我怎麼會喜歡上他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想趁現在聊聊戀愛..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 從以前開始就不擅長撒謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府發佈新一輪避難命令的區域是以下這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然手機等通訊設備依然難以接通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我聽說死神實行的並不是無差別的殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是通過某些條件進行篩選..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:02.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對節目中出現的不適合的言辭向觀眾表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！太不負責任了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不等於說責任在於受害者了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須故意打破死神界和人間界的間隔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓缺乏的魔力得到補充..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我得救這種事..實在太自私了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還醒著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊..用一週的時間能做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你..說這種想早早放棄的臺詞幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所剩不多的時間 不留遺憾地用掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做算是一種放棄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你的性命由我來..！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我說不定算很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！聽我說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最後的最後遇見妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少能再早一點發覺的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對妳..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我對你..可沒那種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接受美菜的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的性命得到延續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想實現你我之間的約定而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的致鬱展開..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是終於來了！傲蘿的眼鏡娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.21,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(685,660)}傲嬌+蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！根據我的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫下眼鏡之後淫亂本性全開之類的..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼放下頭髮之後會變敏感之類的..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色情的妄想請克制一下
